\n打手做到你咁失敗"},{"pid":"35e219defb96f17ed13090330b2c0012157395d9","tid":346291,"uid":30857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:23:31.000Z","msg":"條女濃妝男人樣 打手又蠢過閪"},{"pid":"deed7c122609854c498843636c4dfcdabc57c482","tid":346291,"uid":53207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:25:28.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭閪<br />\n又開post"},{"pid":"718012808cc5c13f58b0521e94b8c56c774d3eb5","tid":346291,"uid":71315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:27:24.000Z","msg":"個打手真係打得好撚肉酸，<br />\n我諗應該就係個老細黎"},{"pid":"f37344b18eda551a06bd01b346b64171fe792f4f","tid":346291,"uid":39347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:32:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>今日先行過 <br />\n因為劏太細 根本勁難用<br />\n個門口又做到勁娘勁老套<br />\n同老深d 死場差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同荃灣地皇一樣，一層劏幾十格劏死個場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認真 講偏佢個位唔算偏 而且人流都旺<br />\n個個都要係佢門口等過馬路<br />\n但首先個門面已經好唔開胃 <br />\n個四粒紅色字真係...唔知以為返左90年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後d 鋪又間到鬼死咁細 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為家住藍田 附近就有個劏場(匯景)<br />\n我真係可以好肯定咁講 只有業主自己跟市場需要而間既劏鋪 先會發到笑<br />\n呢d 唔係跟市場需要間既劏鋪 十間有九間場會俾佢間死"},{"pid":"41da861aef6bd99ff893fd7c79d583ad4cc2bb0f","tid":346291,"uid":1065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:39:59.000Z","msg":"抵死啦<br />\n根本係個發展商自己一手做成"},{"pid":"58d06f86ef7d9950e361317b432cb47098738dea","tid":346291,"uid":44980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:43:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抵死啦<br />\n根本係個發展商自己一手做成</blockquote><br />\n賣左唔跌九成點收返d舖又合又劏"}]}